data.description: Welcome to this absolute STUNNER. 4529 Beat Rd is a beautiful home that has been completely updated. It has 6 beds, 3 baths and 3 acres nestled right here in Litchfield. Walking in the front door you are greeted by the spacious living room that has a gorgeous brick fireplace. To the right down the hall you will find your laundry room, and your breathtaking private primary bedroom/newly remodeled bathroom! The current owners converted what used to be the 7th bedroom into a large attached walk-in closet, and need we say more? It is stunning. Walking back towards the living room you will see your large kitchen and dining room, complete with tons of cabinets and countertop space. Keep going down the hall and you will find your spacious 5 remaining bedrooms and bathrooms. With this home you can choose to relax under your brand new covered patio looking out to your fenced in yard and chicken coop, or on your amazing front porch overlooking the 1/2 acre pond. Which by the way is fully stocked! Updates include new paint and trim throughout, Furnace/HVAC (2023), Windows (2021), Luxury Vinyl in the main living area (2020), Garage floor epoxy (2021), Patio and cover out back (2023), and so much more. See attachments for all information. Don’t miss out on this AMAZING opportunity to call this place home.
